  "title": "Sharing perspectives on public-private sector interaction Proceedings of a workshop, 10 April 2001 ICRISAT, Patancheru, India",
  "abstract": "This book presents several papers presented at a workshop to gather perspectives on the patterns of interaction between private and public agricultural research institutions. The importance of research partnerships, the types of interaction that are possible, and some new ways of exploring this from a policy perspective, are explained.",
